OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784263661
OL,3,CRare Jacobite-era pistols to be
OL,4,Creunited for first time in decades in
OL,5,Cexhibition
OL,7,FTwo rare Jacobite era pistols
OL,8,Frepresenting a "tumultuous" period of
OL,9,FScottish history are to be reunited
OL,10,Ffor the first time in more than 30
OL,11,Fyears in a new exhibition.
OL,13,FDating to the late 17th century, the
OL,14,Fweapons are rare surviving examples of
OL,15,Fwork by the gunmaker and goldsmith
OL,16,FWilliam Lyndsay the Elder of Montrose
OL,17,Fin Angus.
OL,26,@pD@POUpD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
