OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784263661
OL,3,CRare Jacobite-era pistols to be
OL,4,Creunited for first time in decades in
OL,5,Cexhibition
OL,7,FExperts said they are likely to have
OL,8,Fbelonged to a wealthy and influential
OL,9,Flocal family at a time when the town
OL,10,Fwas renowned as a Jacobite stronghold.
OL,12,FIt is believed they were taken to
OL,13,FFrance following the failed Jacobite
OL,14,Fuprising of 1715 and remained there
OL,15,Ffor more than 200 years.
OL,17,FThe pistols came to light in France in
OL,18,F1993, when they came up for sale and
OL,19,Fwere acquired separately by National
OL,20,FMuseums Scotland (NMS) and Montrose
OL,21,FMuseum.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784263661
OL,3,CRare Jacobite-era pistols to be
OL,4,Creunited for first time in decades in
OL,5,Cexhibition
OL,7,FThey are now being reunited for the
OL,8,Ffirst time in more than 30 years in
OL,9,FTartan & Turmoil: The Angus Jacobite
OL,10,FStory where the pistol on loan from
OL,11,FNMS will be displayed alongside its
OL,12,Fpair.
OL,14,FElla Paul, curator, Renaissance and
OL,15,FEarly Modern History at NMS, said:
OL,16,F"These finely crafted pistols are
OL,17,Fextremely rare and I'm delighted we
OL,18,Fhave the opportunity to reunite them.
OL,26,@xD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784263661
OL,3,CRare Jacobite-era pistols to be
OL,4,Creunited for first time in decades in
OL,5,Cexhibition
OL,7,F"They represent a tumultuous period of
OL,8,FScottish history and the experiences
OL,9,Fof the Jacobite families forced into
OL,10,Fexile across Europe.
OL,12,F"We're grateful for the support of
OL,13,FPostcode Lottery players which allows
OL,14,FNational Museums Scotland to share the
OL,15,FNational Collection with audiences
OL,16,Facross the country, bringing these
OL,17,Fremarkable moments in Scotland's past
OL,18,Fto life in a tangible and inspiring
OL,19,Fway."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOU{D@EO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
