FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784263661
OL,3,CRare Jacobite-era pistols to be
OL,4,Creunited for first time in decades in
OL,5,Cexhibition
OL,7,FThe steel heart butt pistols are
OL,8,Frichly decorated with intricate floral
OL,9,Fengravings and silver mounts, and are
OL,10,Fstamped with Lyndsay's mark.
OL,12,FThe exhibition, Tartan & Turmoil, will
OL,13,Fexplore the pivotal role Angus played
OL,14,Fin Jacobite efforts to restore the
OL,15,FStuart dynasty to the throne, with the
OL,16,Fport of Montrose once described as
OL,17,F"the most disloyal and disaffected
OL,18,Ftown in Scotland".
OL,26,@yD@AOUzD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784263661
OL,3,CRare Jacobite-era pistols to be
OL,4,Creunited for first time in decades in
OL,5,Cexhibition
OL,7,FThe pistols will go on show alongside
OL,8,Fitems such as treasures once owned by
OL,9,FStuart kings, intimate letters and
OL,10,Feveryday objects that illustrate
OL,11,Fstories of the Jacobite rebellion
OL,12,Fthroughout Angus.
OL,14,FEmma Gilliland, Museums & Galleries
OL,15,FCollections Lead at ANGUSalive, which
OL,16,Fruns the Montrose Museum, said: "We're
OL,17,Freally excited to bring Angus's
OL,18,FJacobite story to life for visitors.
OL,26,@xD@aOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784263661
OL,3,CRare Jacobite-era pistols to be
OL,4,Creunited for first time in decades in
OL,5,Cexhibition
OL,7,F"Everyone has heard about the
OL,8,FJacobites and Bonnie Prince Charlie,
OL,9,Fbut the vital role that Angus played
OL,10,Fin the risings is little known.
OL,12,F"Some Jacobite objects from our
OL,13,Fcollection are being exhibited for the
OL,14,Fvery first time, and we will also be
OL,15,Fshowcasing significant objects on loan
OL,16,Ffrom leading national institutions.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOU
