PN,30608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784263661
OL,3,CRare Jacobite-era pistols to be
OL,4,Creunited for first time in decades in
OL,5,Cexhibition
OL,7,F"We're incredibly grateful to National
OL,8,FMuseums Scotland for their support
OL,9,Fwith this ` reuniting our Jacobite
OL,10,Fpistol with its pair is a really
OL,11,Fspecial part of the exhibition."
OL,13,FTartan & Turmoil: The Angus Jacobite
OL,14,FStory opens on July 17 and runs until
OL,15,FNovember 23 this year.
OL,17,FThe pistol is on loan to Montrose
OL,18,FMuseum from National Museums Scotland
OL,19,Fwith the support of Postcode Lottery
OL,20,Fplayers.
